---
// src/components/Sustainability.astro
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import sustentaImg from '../assets/sustentabilidade-nicopel.jpg';
import reciclagemImg from '../assets/reciclagem-aparas.jpg';
import insumosImg from '../assets/insumos-naturais.jpg';
---

<section class="relative min-h-[700px] flex flex-col justify-center py-24 overflow-hidden">
  
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
     <Image 
        src={sustentaImg} 
        alt="Floresta sustentável" 
        class="w-full h-full object-cover scale-105"
     />
     <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-black/90 via-black/60 to-black/40"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
    
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-start mb-20"> 
      
      <div>
        <div class="mb-8">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-[#B8E900]/20 border border-[#B8E900]/40 text-xs font-bold text-[#B8E900] mb-6 backdrop-blur-sm shadow-sm">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#B8E900] animate-pulse"></span>
                RESPONSABILIDADE REAL
            </div>
            
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-6 tracking-tight leading-tight drop-shadow-xl">
            Crescimento que respeita <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-[#B8E900] to-[#8bb300]">o planeta e as pessoas.</span>
            </h2>
            
            <p class="text-lg text-white/90 mb-6 leading-relaxed font-medium drop-shadow-md">
            Na Nicopel, acreditamos que uma embalagem premium deve proteger o produto sem agredir o meio ambiente. Utilizamos matéria-prima de fontes renováveis e investimos em tecnologias limpas.
            </p>

            <p class="text-lg text-white leading-relaxed border-l-4 border-[#B8E900] pl-4 italic drop-shadow-md bg-black/20 p-2 rounded-r-lg backdrop-blur-sm">
            Mais do que números, somos feitos de pessoas. Geramos mais de <strong>180 empregos diretos</strong>, apoiando centenas de famílias em nossa região.
            </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-4">
            <div class="bg-black/30 backdrop-blur-md p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/20 flex gap-4 items-start hover:bg-black/50 transition-all shadow-xl">
                <div class="text-[#B8E900] mt-1 drop-shadow-md">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-white text-xl mb-2 drop-shadow-sm">Matéria-Prima Certificada</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-200 leading-relaxed font-medium">Papel proveniente de florestas 100% plantadas e renováveis.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-black/30 backdrop-blur-md p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/20 flex gap-4 items-start hover:bg-black/50 transition-all shadow-xl">
                <div class="text-[#B8E900] mt-1 drop-shadow-md">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-white text-xl mb-2 drop-shadow-sm">Produção Eco-Eficiente</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-200 leading-relaxed font-medium">Maquinário de ponta com menor consumo de energia e redução de resíduos.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-black/30 backdrop-blur-md p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/20 flex gap-4 items-start hover:bg-black/50 transition-all shadow-xl">
                <div class="text-[#B8E900] mt-1 drop-shadow-md">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-white text-xl mb-2 drop-shadow-sm">Substituição do Plástico</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-200 leading-relaxed font-medium">Embalagens biodegradáveis alinhadas com o consumidor consciente.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">

        <div class="group relative h-[400px] rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl transition-all border border-white/10 hover:border-[#B8E900]/50">
            <Image
            src={reciclagemImg}
            alt="Processo de reciclagem de aparas de papel"
            class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110"
            />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black via-black/70 to-transparent"></div>

            <div class="absolute bottom-0 p-8">
            <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 mb-4 rounded-full bg-[#B8E900]/20 text-[#B8E900] text-xs font-bold tracking-wider uppercase backdrop-blur-md">
                Economia Circular
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-3">
                Ciclo Fechado: <span class="text-[#B8E900]">Nada se Perde.</span>
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-base">
                Transformamos 100% das sobras e aparas de nossa produção em novos recursos. Na Nicopel, cada fragmento ganha uma nova vida, garantindo desperdício zero.
            </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group relative h-[400px] rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl transition-all border border-white/10 hover:border-[#B8E900]/50">
            <Image
            src={insumosImg}
            alt="Folha verde representando insumos naturais"
            class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110"
            />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black via-black/70 to-transparent"></div>

            <div class="absolute bottom-0 p-8">
            <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 mb-4 rounded-full bg-[#B8E900]/20 text-[#B8E900] text-xs font-bold tracking-wider uppercase backdrop-blur-md">
                Tecnologia Natural
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-3">
                Insumos Limpos: <span class="text-[#B8E900]">Segurança Real.</span>
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-base">
                Segurança para quem produz e consome. Utilizamos exclusivamente tintas atóxicas e cola orgânica à base de mandioca, eliminando químicos nocivos do processo.
            </p>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>